# Antigravity Brain (Socialise)

**Full reference**: `ANTIGRAVITY_BRAIN.md`. Follow it for design and architecture.

## Design
- **Palette**: Primary `#E2725B` (terracotta), Secondary `#2D5F5D` (teal), Accent `#F4B942`, Paper `#F9F7F2`, Text `#1A1C1C`, Muted `#5C6363`. No pure white backgrounds.
- **Fonts**: Outfit (headings), Quicksand (body).
- **Contrast**: Never white text on paper/secondary backgrounds; use `text-secondary` or `text-primary`. Inputs must have `color: var(--text)`.
- **UI**: Heavy roundness (`rounded-[24px]`/`rounded-[32px]` for cards/modals). Modals: `bg-secondary/60 backdrop-blur-sm`, paper content. Light mode only.

## Stack & patterns
- React 19 + Vite, Tailwind 4, Framer Motion, Lucide. Maps: `@react-google-maps/api` + `use-places-autocomplete`; `LocationPicker.jsx`; graceful failure if `VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY` missing.
